---
---
<section class="example-section" id="example">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="example-header reveal">
      <p class="section-tag">A Real Example</p>
      <h2 class="section-headline">See what we built for <em>Klara Farkas.</em></h2>
    </div>

    <div class="example-grid">
      <div class="example-img-wrap reveal">
        <img
          src="/images/klarity-screenshot.jpg"
          alt="Screenshot of klarityinternational.com — Klara Farkas executive communication coaching website"
          width="600"
          height="450"
          loading="lazy"
        />
        <span class="live-badge">Live Site</span>
      </div>

      <div class="example-story reveal">
        <p>
          Klara is an executive communication coach in Orange County with a decade of corporate
          experience at Yum! Brands and UCI's Paul Merage School. Her original website — built
          in 2014 — had become something she avoided linking to.
        </p>
        <p>
          Two weeks later, she had a site that actually reflects the caliber of her work. Clean,
          mobile-friendly, and positioned to bring in new clients.
        </p>

        <div class="example-meta">
          <div class="example-stat">
            <span class="example-stat-value">$0</span>
            <span class="example-stat-label">Upfront cost</span>
          </div>
          <div class="example-stat">
            <span class="example-stat-value">2 wks</span>
            <span class="example-stat-label">Discovery to launch</span>
          </div>
          <div class="example-stat">
            <span class="example-stat-value">$75</span>
            <span class="example-stat-label">Per month ongoing</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <a
          href="https://klarityinternational.com"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="btn btn-outline"
        >
          View the live site →
        </a>

        <div class="example-testimonial">
          <p><em>Real client testimonial coming soon.</em></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
